# ============================================================================
# NOTES FOR STUDENTS
# ============================================================================
#
# ðŸ’¡ How to use .gitignore:
#
# 1. *.txt means "ignore all .txt files"
# 2. folder/ means "ignore this entire folder"
# 3. !important.txt means "except this file, DO track it"
# 4. **/*.log means "ignore .log files in any subfolder"
#
# ðŸ“š Common patterns:
#
# - Use # for comments
# - One pattern per line
# - Wildcards: * (any characters), ? (one character)
# - Negate patterns with !
#
# ============================================================================
